title: Catwalk models put cancer in spotlight - BBC News
text:
Media playback is unsupported on your device Catwalk models put cancer in spotlight 12 February 2017 Last updated at 08:59 GMT 
Cancer patients took to the catwalk as part of New York Fashion Week. 
The event was organised by Say Yes to Hope a charity which provides support for people with advanced cancer. Related Topics
